article.headline: Chattanooga beats Montreat in 108-51 blowout
article.story: CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -- Gee McGee scored 16 points on 6-of-7 shooting and Chattanooga shot 55.7 percent from the field in a 108-51 victory over Montreat on Saturday. Z. Mason added 15 points and 12 rebounds for the Mocs (2-1). Alex Bran had a career-high 13 points, Casey Jones finished with 12 and Martynas Bareika 11. Chattanooga led 55-34 at the half and opened the second half with a 10-point run. La'Bris Adams had 17 points for Montreat (3-3). The Cavaliers shot 37.3 percent.
